high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left, go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right and face the counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Move a bit to the right,  turn left
Put the knife in the cupboard
Go forward a bit, turn right
Pick up a lettuce slice from the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the sink
Put the lettuce slice in the sink, wash the lettuce slice with water, pick up the lettuce slice from the sink
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the lettuce slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce, wash a slice of lettuce and put it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right to face the closer head of lettuce on the counter.
Slice the closer head of lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn left to face the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Place the knife in the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Turn right to face the sliced lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and remove it.
Turn to the right to face the fridge.
Place the slice of lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of lettuce plus place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter, right of the toaster.
Turn right, move to the counter, left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce, on the counter, on the left.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the stove.
Put the knife in the lower cabinet.
Turn right, move to the counter, left of the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
